# Per-source API keys for `simulate.js --direct` (DEV ONLY).
#
# Copy to keys.env (gitignored) and fill with the one-time keys you get from
# Portal → Ingress → + NEW SOURCE (or RPC ingress.source.create).
#
# Key name = SRC_<source>, where <source> matches samples/<source>.json and the
# ingress source name. Example:
#
#   SRC_github=ingk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#   SRC_stripe=ingk_yyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy
#   SRC_order=ingk_zzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz
